description:
&lt;p&gt;An opportunity has arisen for an enthusiastic, self-motivated, flexible individual to join the Corporate Hub team based at Beckside Court. The role will be to provide an excellent customer focused Head Office reception service and administrative support to Corporate teams&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a well-organised administrator who has excellent customer service, communication and IT skills (including knowledge of Microsoft Office). The successful candidate will be able to efficiently support colleagues and prioritise their own workload, work confidentially, be caring and professional and strive to provide excellent customer service. The role is extremely varied and interesting and would suit someone who would enjoy a busy and challenging workload.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be fully supported in your role and be expected to work to Locala’s organisational values.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The hours for this post are 22.5 hours over Monday to Friday, with the possibility of additional hours&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing Date: Sunday 15th November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;For further details or informal chat please contact Jan Garfitt &lt;/em&gt;by emailing: &lt;span&gt;Janet.Garfitt@locala.org.uk&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Candidates will be invited for an interview on: Thursday 26 November 2020&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
